6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></div></div><div class=\"absolute\" style=\"left:85%;top:80%;opacity:0;transform:scale(0)\"><div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-500\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 text-center max-w-4xl mb-5\"><div class=\"mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/30 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4\">👋 Hi there!</span></div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6 leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\">I&#x27;m<!-- --> <span class=\"text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400\">Milton Ngala</span><br/><span class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400\">a Software Engineer</span><br/><span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent\"></span></h1><div class=\"mb-8 flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><img alt=\"Hero\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-full\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fngala.29c27c02.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fngala.29c27c02.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fngala.29c27c02.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Open to meaningful conversations and new opportunities,<!-- --> <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200\">I design and build software that solves real-world problems</span>.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono font-medium hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.8)\">Next.js 14</span><span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono font-medium hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.8)\">React 18</span><span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono font-medium hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.8)\">.NET Core</span><span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono font-medium hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.8)\">Node.js</span><span class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono font-medium hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:hover:bg-primary-900/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.8)\">+ much more</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><a href=\"/work\"><button class=\"bg-primary-600 dark:bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-heading font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary-700 dark:hover:bg-primary-600 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg\" tabindex=\"0\">See My Work<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right \"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a><button class=\"bg-transparent border-2 border-primary-600 dark:border-primary-400 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-heading font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary-600 dark:hover:bg-primary-400 hover:text-white dark:hover:text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar \"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>Book a Consultation</button></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><a href=\"/about\"><button class=\"text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors duration-300\"></button></a></div></div><section id=\"value-proposition\" class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 mt-14\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 prose prose-lg max-w-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-heading font-bold\">Proven Results That Matter</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4\">Delivering enterprise-grade solutions with measurable impact for businesses of all sizes</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16\"><div class=\"text-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary-100 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up w-10 h-10 text-primary-500\"><polyline points=\"22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17\"></polyline><polyline points=\"16 7 22 7 22 13\"></polyline></svg></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2\" style=\"transform:scale(0)\">12+</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1\">Apps Delivered</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm\">Successfully launched applications</p></div><div class=\"text-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary-100 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-10 h-10 text-primary-500\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2\" style=\"transform:scale(0)\">40%</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1\">Performance Gain</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm\">Average improvement in app performance</p></div><div class=\"text-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary-100 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check-circle w-10 h-10 text-primary-500\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2\" style=\"transform:scale(0)\">100%</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1\">On-Time Delivery</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm\">Projects delivered on schedule</p></div><div class=\"text-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-full w-20 h-20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary-100 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award w-10 h-10 text-primary-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle><path d=\"M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2\" style=\"transform:scale(0)\">5★</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1\">Client Rating</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm\">Average client satisfaction score</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)\"><div class=\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-200 hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm\">Microsoft Certified</span></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-200 hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm\">Azure Solutions Architect</span></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-200 hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm\">React Specialist</span></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-200 hover:bg-primary-50 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm\">Enterprise Ready</span></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none bg-primary-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12\"><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 leading-relaxed mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">I&#x27;ve worked with startups and regional governments to design digital solutions that make a measurable impact from helping clinics cut wait times to mapping 100,000 homes for utility access.</p><p class=\"text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 leading-relaxed mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">My approach combines technical depth with practical problem-solving. I believe the best software doesn&#x27;t just work, it makes people&#x27;s lives easier and businesses more efficient.</p><p class=\"text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 leading-relaxed mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">When I&#x27;m not coding, you&#x27;ll find me exploring Nairobi&#x27;s tech scene, contributing to open source projects, or mentoring junior developers.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12\"><div class=\"text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mx-auto mb-3\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle><path d=\"M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2\">Microsoft Certified</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200\">Azure Solutions Architect Expert</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mx-auto mb-3\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2\">Based in Nairobi</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400\">Working with global clients</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mx-auto mb-3\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2\">Always Learning</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400\">Staying current with tech trends</p></div></div><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a href=\"/contact\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium transition-colors duration-200\">Get in touch →</button></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"><header class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h3 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4\">Selected Case Studies</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Production systems built to solve real business problems and deliver measurable results.</p></header><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 p-8\"><div class=\"relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-2